<body>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <h3 class="text-center">SIGA MANPOWER GROP.</h3>
      <h4 class="text-center">BIO-DATA OF FOREIGN DOMESTIC WORKER (FDW) 家庭管家简历</h4>
      <p class="text-left">*Please ensure that you run through the information within the bio-data as it is an important document to help you
        select a suitable FDW</p>
      <p class="text-left">(A) PROFILE OF FDW</p>
      <p class="text-left">A1 Personal Information个人资料</p>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-xs-6">
        <span>1. Name姓名:<%=name %></span>
        <br>
        <span>2. Date of birth生日:<%=birthdate %></span>
        <br>
        <span>3. Place of birth出生地:<%=birthPlace %></span>
        <br>
        <span>4. Height &weight:</span>
        <span><%=height %> cm</span>
        <span><%=weight %> kgs</span>
        <br>
        <span>5. Residential address in home country居住地址:<%=residentAddress %></span>
        <br>
        <span>6. Name of port / airport to be repatriated to出发口岸:<%=airportName %></span>
        <br>
        <span>7. Contact number in home country联系电话:<%=contactNumber %></span>
        <br>
        <span>8. Cellphone:<%=cellphone %></span>
        <br>
        <span>9. EmailAddress:<%=emailAddress %></span>
        <br>
        <span>10. Religion宗教:<%=religion %></span>
        <br>
        <span>11. Education level教育水平:<%=educationLevel %></span>
        <br>
        <span>12. Number of siblings家中排行:<%=numberSibling %></span>
        <br>
        <span>13. Marital status婚姻状况:<%=maritalStatus %></span>
        <br>
        <span>14. Number of children子女人数:<%=numberChildren %></span>
        <br>
        <span> Age(s)of children子女年龄 (if any):<%=ageChildren %></span>
        <br>
        <span>A2 Medical History/Dietary Restrictions医疗病史</span>
        <br>
        <span>15. Allergies过敏原 (if any):<%=allergies %></span>
        <br>
        <span>A3 Others 其他</span>
        <br>
        <br> SKILLS OF FDW经验技能
      </div>
      <div class="col-xs-6">
        <img id="personImage" src="images/<%= imageSrc %>" class="img-responsive">
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <table class="table table-bordered">
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th scope="col">S/No</th>
            <th scope="col">Areas of Work</th>
            <th scope="col">Experience
              <br>Yes/No
              <br>If yes,state the no. of years
            </th>
            <th scope="col text-center">Assessment/Observation
              <br>Please state qualitative observations of FDW and/or rate the FDW(indicate N.A. of no evaluation was done)
              <br>Poor ......Excellent...N.A.
              <br>1 2 3 4 5 N.A.
            </th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <th scope="row">1.</th>
            <td>Care of infants/children
              <br> Please specify age range:<%=row1col1 %>
            </td>
            <td>
            <%=row1col2 %>
            </td>
            <td>
            <%=row1col3 %>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <th scope="row">2.</th>
            <td>Care of elderly</td>
            <td>
